SiteScout,is,self,serve,advertising,software,for,small,brands,performance,marketers,and,digital,agencies,It,provides,a,straightforward,web,based,platform,that,allows,users,to,create,and,manage,banner,video,and,mobile,ad,campaigns,in,real,time,The,SiteScout,API,uses,REST,calls,to,allow,clients,applications,to,interact,directly,with,SiteScout,systems,The,API,implements,a,wide,range,of,features,which,are,classified,as,Reporting,Audience,Management,or,Campaign,Management,coming,soon